A Quick Tip for Your "Business" Focus:
Since you said you like the business side more, you should aim for roles like GRC Analyst (Governance, Risk, and Compliance), Cybersecurity Consultant, or Pre-Sales Engineer.
These roles require you to know the tech (which you do) but talk the business language (which you like).
